beer.beer_description:
Flows as easy as the perfect cutback on a clean cali barrel.  
Lovingly brewed in the classic USA style.  Aussie malted barley and American cascade hops combine in this well-balanced, refreshing ale with a citrusy kick and strong malty backbone.
